nodes.text: Ketku was a starfighter pilot and member of Red Squadron's Renegade Flight under Commander Narra when the group of fighters were escorting a Rebel convoy that was carrying supplies from Derra IV to Echo Base on Hoth. When the entire convoy was wiped out by the Empire, Ketku was one of the first to be killed, followed shortly by Renegade Leader Narra and a pilot flying under the call sign Renegade Three.
